flipper(matrix): transformed = [] for row in matrix: new_row = [] for element in row: if element <
0: new_row.append(0) elif element %
2
==
0: new_row.append(element *
2) else: new_row.append(element *
3) transformed.append(new_row) result = [ val  for sub in transformed  for val in sub  if val >
5
] return transformed, result
